sentence.Network_en: The lessor can evict the lessee for failure to pay rent.
sentence.Network_cn: 出租人可驱逐不付租金的承租人.

sentence.Network_en: Losses caused intentionally or negligently by the lessee shall be borne by the lessee.
sentence.Network_cn: 如因承租人的故意或过失造成损失的,由承租人负担.

sentence.Network_en: The lessee shall be liable for compensating the lessor for losses suffered as a result thereof.
sentence.Network_cn: 出租人因此所受的损失由承租人负责赔偿.
